Use Case Template 4 :

Name : Chat.

Brief description : The user can chat with an admin.

Players : Admin,User.

Precondition: Logged in successfully.
                   
Basic Flow : 
1. Click on the Chat logo.
2. Discuss with an admin to ask a question

Alternative flow :  He can access to the Chat in the sidebar navigation menu.

Exception flow : ------------------.

Post Conditions : He's redirected to the CNEF's informations when he's finished to discuss.
